{"tid":1079767,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【適得其反】男子純素節吃生豬肉抗議 負責人︰反而鼓勵更多人唔食肉","createTime":"2019-03-27T06:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T09:48:21.000Z","uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"b0ece1ca9b3666d93f0d8143696ca1fca71abd6e","tid":1079767,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"【適得其反】男子純素節吃生豬肉抗議 負責人︰反而鼓勵更多人唔食肉<br />\n<br />\n英國布賴頓市（Brighton）上周六及周日舉行純素食節「VegfestUK」，一名反純素主義男子在場外竟然吃生豬肉抗議，但主辦單位負責人之後透露，有民眾看罷這個令人毛骨悚然的示威後，反而決定不再吃肉，「抗議純素主義似乎實際上變成鼓勵大家」。<br />\n<br />\n從現場拍攝的影片中看到，當時動物權益組織<span style=\"color: red;\">「The Direct Action Everywhere」（DxE）</span>成員高舉<span style=\"color: red;\">「這不是食物，這是暴力」</span>及<span style=\"color: red;\">「吃肉是謀殺」</span>的標語，一名男子拿着一個生豬頭走近他們，然後將豬頭直接放入口中嚙咬。<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位指早知有反純素主義示威者會到場抗議，原以為會有30人，但結果只有3人到場。警方到場警告他們後，護送他們離開。<br />\n<br />\n「VegfestUK」經理巴福德（Tim Barford）說︰「有趣的是，有原本愛吃肉的民眾稱，看到這個令人反感的畫面後，反而決定放棄吃肉，抗議純素主義似乎實際上變成鼓勵大家。」<br />\n<br />\nDxE指出每年逾1000萬隻僅5至6個月大的豬隻被屠宰，去年11月DxE示威者曾衝入牛扒屋高呼<span style=\"color: red;\">「這不是肉，這是暴力」</span>，又播放牛隻被屠宰時的聲音。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"c1b6be7cf9f89ba1492419eb2fc7ec05c332b526","tid":1079767,"uid":54337,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"「這不是食物，這是暴力」<br />\n「吃肉是謀殺」<br />\n<br />\n我想問，係咩野邏輯？"},{"pid":"791b1472406b0124011829f50124b5c611bc22e6","tid":1079767,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:56:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190326/59409190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59409190&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5Uigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=6af46b52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190326%2F59409190&h=32101f68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190326/59409190</a>"},{"pid":"4be1a1ea4b568e2c36258426ae5a0e6c70213499","tid":1079767,"uid":54337,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"c1b6be7cf9f89ba1492419eb2fc7ec05c332b526","tid":1079767,"uid":54337,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"「這不是食物，這是暴力」<br />\n「吃肉是謀殺」<br />\n<br />\n我想問，係咩野邏輯？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"純素撚已經將食肉變成罪行<br />\n下一步呢？<br />\n既然食肉係謀殺，咁食肉要唔要坐監？<br />\n<br />\n班人真係癡撚線"},{"pid":"a75a4a36b0c99f25f1dd52d1f72cb2719c2a7730","tid":1079767,"uid":54337,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:00:15.000Z","msg":"純素食節「VegfestUK」<br />\n<br />\n純素節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />已經進化到宗教，同聖誕節 復活節等等同級<br />\n<br />\n黨同伐異，而且極度排他。班生番癡撚線"},{"pid":"9eb5333cf4963c8bdd5c60f26fe66c6d038efce3","tid":1079767,"uid":33206,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:09:37.000Z","msg":"「VegfestUK」經理巴福德（Tim Barford）說︰「有趣的是，有原本愛吃肉的民眾稱，看到這個令人反感的畫面後，反而決定放棄吃肉，抗議純素主義似乎實際上變成鼓勵大家。」<br />\n<br />\n邊個知？🤷🏻&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"e017070f0f3807e1ee2a7f18afb049ac9fc43ee0","tid":1079767,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:11:31.000Z","msg":"強加於人身上嘅意念就係極權,講完"},{"pid":"1404c5371971ccb67808a887f08e45afa9866beb","tid":1079767,"uid":43510,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:18:25.000Z","msg":"等睇連登仔去狗展食狗肉抗議"},{"pid":"e96391ca8f8ab6e65e4b0c41a60b5c72f84013ec","tid":1079767,"uid":238415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:25:24.000Z","msg":"素食撚其實首先係咪應該要爭取人道毀滅所有肉食動物先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.